&lt;p&gt;With the patch:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/provider/select?q=*%3A*&amp;amp;wt=json&amp;amp;indent=true&amp;amp;fl=provider_json:[json&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/provider/select?q=*%3A*&amp;amp;wt=json&amp;amp;indent=true&amp;amp;fl=provider_json:[json&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;

